Intel Core i5-13600K Desktop Processor 14 (6P+8E) Cores up to 5.10 GHz

 

The Intel 13th Gen Core i5-13600K is a high-performance CPU with 14 cores, split into 6 performance cores and 8 efficiency cores. It can reach speeds of up to 5.10 GHz, making it a great choice for demanding tasks like gaming, content creation, and heavy multitasking.

As a powerful gaming processor, it delivers fast and smooth performance for modern games. Whether you're playing fast-paced action games or immersive open-world titles, this CPU ensures that everything runs without lag or delays. Plus, since it’s unlocked, you can overclock it for even more speed.

Designed for multitasking, the Core i5-13600K handles running multiple apps or tasks at once with ease. It's ideal for gamers who stream or work on other projects while gaming, giving you the flexibility and power you need for everything.
